{"tid":225130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日仲洗唔洗入鄉隨俗？","createTime":"2017-05-01T14:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T08:19:42.000Z","uid":35870,"like":36,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e533460506593e54af29128e2db76ae61fafbc2","tid":225130,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:19:46.000Z","msg":"好似人地太平清譙，唔畀食肉要食齋咁樣，外來人去到食咁合唔合理呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實唔只長洲，香港仲有個d新界圍村一樣會做譙，都係唔食得肉，唔係就會畀人屌老母，甚至好似新聞個呀婆講，以前係會打9你的<br />\n<br />\n但到左今時今日，就算係個d村落本身，都已經住左好多外來人，包括好多鬼佬<br />\n<br />\n如果係一個鬼佬堅持食肉，咁又有無問題呢？村民又可唔可以屌9佢呢？<br />\n<br />\n假如個答案係yes嘅話，咁係咪代表村民係依然有權力？又或者村落入面又凌駕法律嘅規則呢？<br />\n<br />\n又再進一步諗，假如個條村係非常尊敬長輩，長幼有序，d老人家或者上左年紀嘅人通常都係默許可以優先用村落某d車位嘅時候，一個外來人唔小心泊左係呢個車位，又應唔應該畀人屌呢？<br />\n<br />\n又或者根據某d傳統，d圍村人係有權用某d車位，咁若然我唔小心泊左係個個位又得唔得呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢竟就算而家好多村落都唔再係好似以前咁得d村民(好似係因為土地問題)，咁村民嘅潛規則又應唔應該遵守呢？<br />\n<br />\n村民嘅權力又可以去到邊呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:要呀，人地傳統要入鄉隨俗架嘛，尊重d好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:你理撚得我Y,公眾地方黎你吹咩，香港有法律架"},{"pid":"1611aa263dfe42dcd0a88a462802bee48edabc31","tid":225130,"uid":51902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:22:44.000Z","msg":"隨俗係比面你  唔隨係道理"},{"pid":"ff6393b28c2b0f4efba8bb18646ae12436fc64a4","tid":225130,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118a6c80efe3a984a08084f1e47d51ebce3e0c9e","tid":225130,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cabe1a8b2d9a088b477283daeaefeb61a5bc65e","tid":225130,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨俗係比面你  唔隨係道理</blockquote><br />\n你代返大陸人嚟香港隨唔隨俗，睇下啱唔啱"},{"pid":"e4fd825dab80830568e4b8f22aecd44d936fbecf","tid":225130,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"好撚神奇，人地外來人要守齋戒，反而係果度開鋪可以大搖大擺賣，然後屌個食既而唔係賣果個"},{"pid":"83f834bd7c3f007f514ac1d470b137ce2bcd7b6f","tid":225130,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9977437f0edd77698d92271e927a9fb73897d52","tid":225130,"uid":106868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"耶撚表示： 我信基督教嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非耶"},{"pid":"fc652a516f1f68a95667001e0dbf9d1a0728b59e","tid":225130,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"冇話權唔權力，屌鳩你係佢嘅意見，你聽唔聽係另一回事。"},{"pid":"81c0f02da2d06fa56ced2d4bd1d22bd434ee9203","tid":225130,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:26:44.000Z","msg":"當然要啦<br />\n抗拒嘅就唔好去<br />\n否則同支那蝗有咩分別"},{"pid":"9d3c9bf59026c36c2ddcfe064ecace960d84b8cb","tid":225130,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨俗係比面你  唔隨係道理</blockquote><br />\n正如係到唔用5p字係俾面你 用就係道理"},{"pid":"6c4ed73450ecb66380ef5131b2e86987d312acef","tid":225130,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:30:42.000Z","msg":"亂泊圍村車位你架車唔洗要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6248b199af278cc8209a2bfc48f503fa1c183a","tid":225130,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨俗係比面你  唔隨係道理</blockquote><br />\n大陸人：落來香港講廣東話係比面你  唔講係道理"},{"pid":"70e1421173aa3a63ed422e84732a54146e1a74f8","tid":225130,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:49:45.000Z","msg":"一係就明確劃分領地全村自己人<br />\n唔係的話你俾外人入嚟住<br />\n又要管人生活方式唔合理"},{"pid":"4941bfd9cf6be11264fd7c521f2b78efe8d4b946","tid":225130,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係就明確劃分領地全村自己人<br />\n唔係的話你俾外人入嚟住<br />\n又要管人生活方式唔合理</blockquote><br />\n以後你就味撚屌9大陸人呀周街屙屎"},{"pid":"aa22dff199ab1af15e86ff4819fff7ac9adc1827","tid":225130,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:57:12.000Z","msg":"一個問題見到唔少連登仔其實都係蝗蟲基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8e41060dceda528014a26bbadd3be8da6a34d8","tid":225130,"uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個問題見到唔少連登仔其實都係蝗蟲基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個種我是客人大撚晒feel 出晒來"},{"pid":"9d365a676e339a053c22ace60e7e5b1f592e10a8","tid":225130,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:07:39.000Z","msg":"大家都是中國人"},{"pid":"09f365c70a0cf7dfc7e9f0db04a04583b712c4ba","tid":225130,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:20:21.000Z","msg":"所以大陸人隨地大小便都合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f414a78bfb467cb49765cb0fddffc9dbd93db667","tid":225130,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係就明確劃分領地全村自己人<br />\n唔係的話你俾外人入嚟住<br />\n又要管人生活方式唔合理</blockquote><br />\n以後你就味撚屌9大陸人呀周街屙屎</blockquote><br />\n香港同大陸係兩個國度，受兩種不同法制管轄<br />\n<br />\n但香港嘅村落又係咪同樣道理呢？如果要嘅話係咪即係間接承認村落係村民嘅地方呢？咁村民可唔可以進一步向外來人收稅呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f28b0f3a6e6f1f3469ce1efb2f7fe90f3eea53","tid":225130,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:32:29.000Z","msg":"香港傳統村落嘅齋戒係同其他宗族嘅齋戒唔同嘅<br />\n<br />\n其他宗族係自己食齋即可，但呢d村落，係只要行入村落範圍就唔食得，村民要食又唔係話唔得，但要出村"},{"pid":"54738dc9c84ccf613f9c42f4dabe6f790619d114","tid":225130,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:35:00.000Z","msg":"非法律，係尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尊重都做唔到既話，只係怕法，你既人都幾低層次"},{"pid":"36c08f268b79841779ac963bc61397aff570c076","tid":225130,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>非法律，係尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尊重都做唔到既話，只係怕法，你既人都幾低層次</blockquote><br />\n假如長洲商舖尊重但無左十萬生意額，咁實際上仲做唔做到尊重呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be319cdeb89a7dc2c86981089d893e6229fb5ce4","tid":225130,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>亂泊圍村車位你架車唔洗要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯喇就係我講嘅野，村民權力可以去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965db8d59094d681c0cd4faebe4288fa454e9319","tid":225130,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨俗係比面你  唔隨係道理</blockquote><br />\n你咪俾人踢出門口囉"}]}